Setup to receive periodic notices from the webserver

If pretty URL's are enabled for the website, configure the webserver to call,
at 15-minute intervals:
  [YOURSITEURL]/Cron/send

OR

If pretty URL's are NOT enabled, configure the webserver to call,
at 15-minute intervals:
  [YOURSITEURL]/index.php?mact=Cron,cntnt01,default,0&cntnt01returnid=NUM
where NUM is a valid page-index (typically the id for the default page)

Crontab settings for a linux server and pretty urls e.g.
*/15 * * * * [/path/to/]curl [YOURSITEURL]/Cron/send
OR
*/15 * * * * [/path/to/]curl [YOURSITEURL]/Cron/send 1>/dev/null 2>&1
OR
1,16,31,46 * * * * [/path/to/]curl [YOURSITEURL]/Cron/send

